dct_title_s:
A new and most exact map of Africa described by N.I. Viſcher and don into
          Engliſh enlarged and corrected acording to I Blaen and others with the Habits of ye
          people & ye manner of ye cheife sitties: ye like neuer before
dct_description_sm:
Similar to Blaeu's map (see NOR 0030). The sea is decorated with more ships than usual
        for "maps of this period and the sea monsters are fewer and smaller."
dct_rights_sm: Image from the Dr. Oscar I. Norwich collection of maps of Africa and its islands, 1486 - ca. 1865 courtesy Stanford University Libraries. This item is in the public domain.
